    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <p>Elvira Vogel was an educator with the Washtenaw Intermediate School District.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <p>The Elvira Vogel papers document her participation in various Washtenaw County educational organizations. The Vogel collection has been arranged into series of records for each of these organizations.</p>
    </scopecontent>
