      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Washtenaw Intermediate School District <unitdate type="inclusive" normal="1960/1990">1960-1990</unitdate></unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Washtenaw Intermediate School District (WISD) series (1960-1990) at 5 linear feet is the largest series in the collection and documents Vogel's more than thirty years of service with the school district. Most of her work focused on providing education and vocational training to the physically disabled and children with learning and emotional/behavioral disabilities. The papers strongly reflect this focus. The WISD series consists of a subseries of alphabetical topical files (2 linear feet) and a subseries of printed materials (3 linear feet) relating to the WISD's budgets and special education services. The printed materials span many years, beginning in 1964 and extending up to 1990.</p>
        </scopecontent>
